Uses of Package
com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport

  • Packages that use com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport 
    Package Description
    com.i2group.apollo.events.transport
    Contains classes for the events that commands can fire, as well as classes and interfaces that define changes to the Analysis Repository.
    com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.transport
    Contains classes for communicating information between the services that are responsible for data access on-demand solutions in i2 Analyze.
    com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport
    Contains classes and interfaces for communicating data with i2 Analyze services that interact with the Analysis Repository.
    com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport
    Contains classes for communicating provenance information with i2 Analyze services.
  • Classes in com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport used by com.i2group.apollo.events.transport 
    Class and Description
    CardProvenance
    The provenance of the data on a Card that an Item in i2 Analyze contains.

    Class and Description
    CardProvenance
    The provenance of the data on a Card that an Item in i2 Analyze contains.
    RetrievalBlockGlobalIdentifier
    A container for information that uniquely identifies a RetrievalBlock across multiple CardProvenances.
  • Classes in com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport used by com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport 
    Class and Description
    CardProvenance
    The provenance of the data on a Card that an Item in i2 Analyze contains.
  • Classes in com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport used by com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport 
    Class and Description
    OriginIdentifier
    A container for information that uniquely identifies the data that the CardProvenance with this OriginIdentifier describes, in its original data source.
    RetrievalBlock
    An collection of RetrievalDatums that together contain all the information necessary for i2 Analyze to retrieve the data for a Card from a particular external source.
    RetrievalBlockIdentifier
    A container for information that uniquely identifies a RetrievalBlock within its containing CardProvenance.
    RetrievalDatum
    A key-value pair that contains some or all of the information that i2 Analyze uses to retrieve data from an external source.
